# All values are OPTIONAL. A build with no .env at all gets the full cloud
# experience: Supabase access routes through the sei proxy
# (https://api.sei.gg/supabase), which injects the public anon key
# server-side. Local (BYOK) mode never needed any of these.

# Override the proxy host (e.g. a locally running sei-proxy).
#SEI_PROXY_URL=

# Direct-to-Supabase override for self-hosters running their own Supabase
# project. Set BOTH or NEITHER — a URL with no key sends an unusable
# placeholder key to your project. The anon key is public-by-design;
# RLS is the actual security boundary.
#SUPABASE_URL=
#SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=

# KusArt B2B API key for unique-companion portrait generation
# (https://kusart.com/account → API Keys). Without it, generation still
# succeeds but companions save without portrait/skin art.
#KUSART_API_KEY=
# Override the KusArt API host (default https://api.kusa.pics).
#KUSART_BASE_URL=
